Alerts:
Alerts is popup message . Alerts takes complete focus of our main page that we are working on.
we Cannot proceed until it is handle.

There are main three types of alerts:
1) Web based alerts / HTML alerts-we can simply inspect and perform needed actions.
2) Javascript alerts/browser alerts- we can handle this alerts by using switch to() method. We cannot inspects this types of alerts

3) Windows based alerts- we cannot handle this types of alerts with selenium.

Types of JS alerts:
Simple alerts : we can only click ok.
2) Confirmation alerts- either confirm or cancel
3) prompt alerts -we can perform some types of action on this alerts.


To handle js alerts we only have 4 options
1. accepts();
2.dismiss();
3.getText();
4.sendKeys();

Frames
Frames is a separate independent window in our webpage
 3 ways to interact with frames:
 1. By index
 2.By id or name
 3. By web element
